  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DatasetContext
    A method that instantiates a Dataset at runtime.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DatasetInstantiationException
    This exception is thrown if - for whatever reason - a data set cannot be instantiated at runtime.

Package co.cask.cdap.api.data Description

Defines means of integration between programs and data access. All data access is performed via system or user defined (custom) Datasets.
